ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13941] added command 
``polars len``
 for performing count(
*) like operations
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13939] exposed flag truncate-ragged-lines in 
``polars open``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13904] added command 
``polars profile``
 for profiling lazy dataframes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13879] added 
``polars concat``
 to allow concatenation of multiple dataframes
