[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13938] fixed a Docker image build failure
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13912] made some small tweaks to release and nightly workflow
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13895] added loongarch64-unknown-linux-gnu-gcc build target
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13896] bumped version to 0.98.1
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13883] removed more quotes on external command arguments
