[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13893] fixed 
``inspect``
 and 
``explore``
 panics on empty records
weirdan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13892] made 
``input listen``
 respect 
``$env.config.use_kitty_protocol``
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13890] added search terms to 
``into value``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13857] made Nu only ask to create config files the first time it's started
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13885] fixed 
``try``
 not working with 
``let``
, etc.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13881] fixed 
``do -p``
 not waiting for external commands
fornwall 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13878] bumped rustix from 0.38.34 to 0.38.37
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13859] added content_type metadata to view source
dead10ck 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13830] added binary type support to polars
YizhePKU 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12953] set current working directory at startup
anka-213 
